  keywords  = {Industries;Asia;Prototypes;Information security;Focusing;Machine learning;Planning;Smart grid security;energy grid security;critical infrastructure;Man-in-the-Middle attacks;False Data Injection attacks;automated planning;AI planning;PLC security;cyber-security;cyber resilience;Operational Technology (OT)},
